kraken-tools: tools for automatic trading
=========================================

kraken-tools is a set of tools aiming to assist in automatic trading
on the [kraken exchange](https://www.kraken.com/). It includes
collecting and storing historical exchange data, environment to write
and test trading strategies.

Tool for syncronising private trades with ledger
[ledger](https://github.com/ledger/ledger).

Dependencies
------------

kraken-tools requires a few dependencies.

 + python3.3 or later
 + [krakenex library](https://github.com/veox/python3-krakenex)
 + sqlite, corresponding python library
 
